        "description": "Beam diameter for uniform cleaning; smaller (100-200 μm) for fine surface prep, larger (300-500 μm) for broad areas. Recommended 200 μm for cement to achieve good resolution on rough surfaces. Source: Equipment specifications from Adapt Laser Systems scanners for industrial cleaning; process studies in Lasers in Manufacturing (2019)."
